narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Don't commit academic fraud, keep accurate data, don't screw collaborators out of authorship, and don't commit sexual harrassment.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The biggest weakness is that most of the examples were geared towards a physics lab setting. There were very few examples of difficulties that theorists or observers (in astronomy) might face, which made it difficult for some students to fully engage in that session.
very useful. I think it would be better to give even more examples in the presentation
